{"type":"message","id":"3d866b7b","parentId":"1dc4f1bb","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:00:00.199Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Saturday, May 16th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-05-16 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1778893200197}}
{"type":"message","id":"78be0646","parentId":"3d866b7b","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:02:45.569Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job reminding me of Cursor collaboration rules. The instructions say \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" (no reply needed, silently confirm). So I should just acknowledge and confirm I've noted the rules, without sending a message."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n✅ 已收到每日规则刷新通知。Cursor 协作规则已确认：\n1. submit_task.py 用于提交任务\n2. confirm_write.py 用于处理用户确认回复\n3. --list 查看队列，--results 查看结果\n\n静默确认完成，规则已牢记。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778893200198}}
